# The eslint config sets `linebreak-style: ['error', 'unix']`, and CI runs on
# ubuntu-latest (LF). Windows checkouts default to CRLF (core.autocrlf=true),
# which makes `npm run lint` fail locally while passing in CI.
# Force LF in the working tree for all text files so both agree.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary / generated - never touch line endings
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary
tfplan binary
